public class ProfilStudentLayout extends com.vaadin.flow.component.orderedlayout.VerticalLayout
A layout component that displays and manages the student's profil form. Contains fields for first name, last name, interests, skills, degree, website, profil description, and avatar URL.

This class defines the form layout and organizes the components into horizontal sections.
